{"tid":1822301,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「人權觀察」負責人赴港發表報告遭拒入境：港府令人失望　北京壓力下自由流失","createTime":"2020-01-13T01:15:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T01:55:25.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"76705d7a5074bef618cf41e7ac4632b0abb27ee7","tid":1822301,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T01:15:26.000Z","msg":"人權觀察執行長肯尼士・羅斯（Kenneth Roth）原定赴港出席該組織《2020世界人權報告》發表會，但於昨日（12日）抵港時，遭港府拒絕入境，未有給任何理由。<br />\n<br />\n羅斯表示，「拒絕讓我入境香港正好生動反映了當前問題」，港府的舉動令人失望，亦再次表明北京正在加強壓制香港，進一步限制香港人在「一國兩制」下享有的有限自由。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oZ7ags0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoZ7ags0.png&h=4f8cf359&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mArBWs1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmArBWs1.png&h=eecb851d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人權觀察原本預定在本月 15 日舉行記者會，發表652頁的《2020世界人權報告》當中評鑒 100 個國家的人權情況。羅斯在今年度的導論中特別警告：中國政府正集中火力攻擊全球人權保障體系。由於未能入境，羅斯已將發布會改在 1 月 14 日於紐約聯合國舉行。<br />\n<br />\n羅斯過去曾多次訪問香港，包括 2018 年 4 月赴港發表人權觀察關於中國就業市場性別歧視的研究報告。<br />\n<br />\n去年 11  月27 日，美國總統特朗普簽署《香港人權與民主法案》，12 月 2 日中國宣布對人權觀察等數家設於美國的民主宣導機構。當時北京和香港當局均未進一步說明細節。<br />\n<br />\n根據人權觀察，香港入境當局曾多次拒絕批評大陸或香港政府的訪客入境，包括本月初一名為香港抗爭做紀錄的美籍攝影師，去年 9月 的美籍學者蓋瑞特（Dan Garrett）和2017 年 10 月的英籍香港觀察（Hong Kong Watch）創辦人羅傑斯（Benedict Rogers）。<br />\n<br />\n羅斯又說，中國維權人士經常慘遭監禁、酷刑和強迫失蹤，相形之下，自己被拒絕入境是小事一椿。他指中國干涉人權觀察等國際組織的工作，無異於全球性的言論審查，各國政府應在為時已晚之前起身抵制。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E8%A7%80%E5%AF%9F-%E8%B2%A0%E8%B2%AC%E4%BA%BA%E8%B5%B4%E6%B8%AF%E7%99%BC%E8%A1%A8%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%E9%81%AD%E6%8B%92%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83-%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E4%BB%A4%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%B1%E6%9C%9B-%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%A3%93%E5%8A%9B%E4%B8%8B%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E6%B5%81%E5%A4%B1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25E8%25A7%2580%25E5%25AF%259F-%25E8%25B2%25A0%25E8%25B2%25AC%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25B5%25B4%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2591%258A%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%258B%2592%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25A2%2583-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%259C%259B-%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E5%25A3%2593%25E5%258A%259B%25E4%25B8%258B%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%25E6%25B5%2581%25E5%25A4%25B1%2F&d=EP%2BJfZZVzGvO4DQPpGaiyF8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=f04dee6d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25E8%25A7%2580%25E5%25AF%259F-%25E8%25B2%25A0%25E8%25B2%25AC%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25B5%25B4%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2591%258A%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%258B%2592%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25A2%2583-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%259C%259B-%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E5%25A3%2593%25E5%258A%259B%25E4%25B8%258B%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%25E6%25B5%2581%25E5%25A4%25B1%2F&h=f66a1ee2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E8%A7%80%E5%AF%9F-%E8%B2%A0%E8%B2%AC%E4%BA%BA%E8%B5%B4%E6%B8%AF%E7%99%BC%E8%A1%A8%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%E9%81%AD%E6%8B%92%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83-%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E4%BB%A4%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%B1%E6%9C%9B-%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%A3%93%E5%8A%9B%E4%B8%8B%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E6%B5%81%E5%A4%B1/</a>"},{"pid":"837654447226221626601fa45a49ed249dc719dc","tid":1822301,"uid":68689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T01:19:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/p960x960/78831821_10158360324917448_1800553769130262528_o.png?_nc_cat=110&amp;_nc_ohc=2UGWMOshiXkAX9bSWOL&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;oh=9e21c8f33bcdb7d61d04644173b9eef0&amp;oe=5EA33D1B\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fp960x960%2F78831821_10158360324917448_1800553769130262528_o.png